              def encrypt(string, pwd)
          
      96. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    96. 
            

            

                @salt = OpenSSL::Random.random_bytes(16)
          
      97. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    97. 
            

            

                # prepare cipher for encryption
          
      98. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    98. 
            

            

                e = OpenSSL::Cipher.new('AES-128-CBC')
          
      99. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    99. 
            

            

                e.encrypt
          
      100. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    100. 
            

            

                # next, generate a PKCS5-based string for your key + initialization vector
          
      101. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    101. 
            

            

                key_iv = OpenSSL::PKCS5.pbkdf2_hmac_sha1(pwd, @salt, 1024, e.key_len + e.iv_len)
          
      102. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    102. 
            

            

                key = key_iv[0, e.key_len]
          
      103. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    103. 
            

            

                @iv = key_iv[e.key_len, e.iv_len]
          
      104. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    104. 
            

            

                # now set the key and iv for the encrypting cipher
          
      105. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    105. 
            

            

                e.key = key
          
      106. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    106. 
            

            

                e.iv  = @iv
          
      107. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    107. 
            

            

                # encrypt the data!
          
      108. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    108. 
            

            

                encrypted = String.new << e.update(string) << e.final
          
      109. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    109. 
            

            

                [encrypted, @iv, @salt].map { |v| ::Base64.strict_encode64(v) }
          
      110. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    110. 
            

            

              end

                def build_resource

                    @resource.provider   = provider
          
      115. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    115. 
            

            

                    @resource.password = (0...8).map { rand(65..90).chr }.join
          
      116. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    116. 
            

            

                    @resource.is_new_user = true
          
      117. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    117. 
            

            

                    # honor devise configuration for case_insensitive_keys
          
      118. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    118. 
            

            

                    @resource.email = if resource_class.case_insensitive_keys.include?(:email)
          
      119. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    119. 
            

            

                                        sign_up_params[:email].try(:downcase)
          
      120. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    120. 
            

            

                                      else
          
      121. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    121. 
            

            

                                        sign_up_params[:email]
          
      122. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    122. 
            

            

                                      end

                def coupon_errors

      133.

                      error = 'Number of users exceeded for given referral code' if total_count >= refer.no_of_users
          
      134. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    134. 
            

            

                    elsif sign_up_params[:referred_by].present? && refer.nil?
          
      135. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    135. 
            

            

                      error = 'Invalid referral code'
          
      136. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    136. 
            

            

                    end

    137. 
            

            

                  elsif sign_up_params[:referred_by].present?
          
      138. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    138. 
            

            

                    if sign_up_params[:referred_by] != @resource.referred_by
          
      139. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    139. 
            

            

                      error = 'Referral code does not matched with existing referral'
          
      140. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    140. 
            

            

                    end

    141. 
            

            

                  end

                def resource_update_method
          
      210. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    210. 
            

            

                  if DeviseTokenAuth.check_current_password_before_update == :attributes
          
      211. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    211. 
            

            

                    'update_with_password'
          
      212. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    212. 
            

            

                  elsif DeviseTokenAuth.check_current_password_before_update == :password && account_update_params.key?(:password)
          
      213. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    213. 
            

            

                    'update_with_password'
          
      214. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    214. 
            

            

                  elsif account_update_params.key?(:current_password)
          
      215. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    215. 
            

            

                    'update_with_password'
          
      216. 
        
      
      
        
      
          
    216. 
            

            

                  else
